TEXT -1488 624 Left 2 !.meas AC fc WHEN mag(((V(tv_num)/V(tv_den))*(V(ti_num)/V(ti_den))-1)/((V(tv_num)/V(tv_den))+(V(ti_num)/V(ti_den))+2))=1 FALL=1\n \n.meas AC phT FIND (((V(tv_num)/V(tv_den))*(V(ti_num)/V(ti_den))-1)/((V(tv_num)/V(tv_den))+(V(ti_num)/V(ti_den))+2)) WHEN mag(((V(tv_num)/V(tv_den))*(V(ti_num)/V(ti_den))-1)/((V(tv_num)/V(tv_den))+(V(ti_num)/V(ti_den))+2))=1 FALL=1\n.meas AC pm PARAM 180+phT
TEXT -2520 -592 Left 2 !.tran 3u
TEXT -3504 -56 Left 2 ;.dc param vid -40m 40m 100u
TEXT -2752 696 Left 2 !* 1. Find the starting baseline right before the step\n.meas tran V_base FIND V(vop1,vom1) AT=1.9u\n \n* 2. Find the settled final value long after the step\n.meas tran V_final FIND V(vop1,vom1) AT=2.9u\n \n* 3. Calculate the total swing and the 10% / 90% thresholds\n.meas tran V_swing PARAM V_final-V_base\n.meas tran V10 PARAM V_base + 0.1*V_swing\n.meas tran V90 PARAM V_base + 0.9*V_swing\n \n* 4. Measure the time between the calculated thresholds\n.meas tran true_rise_time TRIG V(vop1,vom1) VAL=V10 RISE=1 TARG V(vop1,vom1) VAL=V90 RISE=1
